        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41427421/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41427421/" class="">第20页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/105594691/" class=" " title="翊夕">翊夕</a>
                (等到看你银色满际)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="41427421">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">官班制中记别驾、从事班位，等差有序，分六等二十三州；大同中朱异作五等，一等为二十州。按陈官品中有东扬州为一等，而东扬州为普通中置，疑朱“上品二十州”为割裂天监时前五等十九州并加东扬州而成。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-01-29 14:14</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                官班制中记别驾、从事班位，等差有序，分六等二十三州；大同中朱异作五等，一等为二十州。按陈官品中有东扬州为一等，而东扬州为普通中置，疑朱“上品二十州”为割裂天监时前五等十九州并加东扬州而成。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41427421/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2017-01-29 14:14
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="41427409">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/105594691/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u105594691-20.jpg" alt="翊夕" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41427409/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41427409/" class="">第21页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/105594691/" class=" " title="翊夕">翊夕</a>
                (等到看你银色满际)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="41427409">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">两个问题：
1.流内十四班到流内三班共计十二等，并非十等；
2.官班不是官品，而是起源于朝班，官班实施后官品不废，班位与官品并不能完全对应，故而郡守在官班中的等级并不能完全与官品对应；</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-01-29 14:09</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                两个问题：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>1.流内十四班到流内三班共计十二等，并非十等；<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2.官班不是官品，而是起源于朝班，官班实施后官品不废，班位与官品并不能完全对应，故而郡守在官班中的等级并不能完全与官品对应；
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







